name: CADAI
description: CADAICO is transforming the CAD (Computer-Aided Design) industry by tackling inefficiencies in engineering design processes with a combination of AI and blockchain technology. The CADAI Token is the native utility token of the CADAI Platform and Ecosystem. As a multi-faceted digital asset with a fixed supply of 100 million, the $CADAI token plays a vital role in securing the network, providing a medium for fees, and aligning stakeholder initiatives.
